{"sections":[{"estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","kind":"hero","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]}],"backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","title":"Going further with more resources","chapter":"Go further with more ressources"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"contentSection":[{"kind":"contentAndMedia","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"stepsSection":[{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get it at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon finder"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is also available there to 